---
// Article 1.2: Royal Malaysian Police (PDRM)
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import AudienceTabs from '../../../components/AudienceTabs.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/panduan-rakyat/Breadcrumb';

const articleData = {
  sectionNumber: '01',
  sectionTitle: 'Safety and Emergencies',
  sectionIcon: '🚨',
  articleTitle: 'Royal Malaysian Police (PDRM)',
  articleDescription: 'Police services, reporting procedures, and understanding your rights',
  colorRgb: '220, 38, 38',
  lastUpdated: 'March 2026',
};

const simpleContent = `
  <h2 id="what-is-pdrm">What is PDRM?</h2>
  <p>PDRM (Polis Diraja Malaysia) is the Royal Malaysia Police. They maintain law and order in Malaysia.</p>
  
  <h2 id="emergency-number">Emergency Number</h2>
  <p><strong>Call 999</strong> for police emergencies.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Free from all phones</li>
    <li>Available 24/7</li>
    <li>Multiple languages available</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="when-to-call">When to Call Police</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>🚨 Crime in progress</li>
    <li>🚨 Accident with injuries</li>
    <li>🚨 Threat to safety</li>
    <li>🚨 Suspicious activity</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="police-station">Visiting a Police Station</h2>
  <p>Go to the nearest police station to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Make a police report</li>
    <li>Report lost items/documents</li>
    <li>Report scams or fraud</li>
    <li>Collect clearance letters</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="important-numbers">Important Numbers</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>999</strong> - Emergency</li>
    <li><strong>03-2115 9999</strong> - KL Police HQ</li>
    <li><strong>15999</strong> - Bukit Aman (toll-free)</li>
  </ul>
`;

const detailedContent = `
  <h2 id="what-is-pdrm">What is PDRM?</h2>
  <p>The Polis Diraja Malaysia (PDRM) or Royal Malaysia Police is the primary law enforcement agency in Malaysia. Established in 1807, it is one of the oldest police forces in Southeast Asia.</p>

  <h2 id="organizational-structure">Organizational Structure</h2>
  <p>PDRM is headquartered at Bukit Aman in Kuala Lumpur. The force is organized into:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Contingent Police Headquarters (IPK)</strong> - State level</li>
    <li><strong>District Police Headquarters (IPD)</strong> - District level</li>
    <li><strong>Police Stations (Balai Polis)</strong> - Local level</li>
    <li><strong>Police Posts (Rumah Polis)</strong> - Community level</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="emergency-numbers">Emergency Contact Numbers</h2>
  <div class="bg-muted p-4 rounded-lg my-4">
    <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">📞 Police Emergency Contacts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>999</strong> - General emergency (toll-free, 24/7)</li>
      <li><strong>15999</strong> - Bukit Aman hotline (toll-free)</li>
      <li><strong>03-2115 9999</strong> - KL Police Headquarters</li>
      <li><strong>SMS 15888</strong> - For hearing/speech impaired</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="when-to-call">When to Call Police</h2>
  <h3>Emergency Situations (Call 999):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>🚨 Crime in progress (robbery, burglary, assault)</li>
    <li>🚨 Traffic accidents with injuries or fatalities</li>
    <li>🚨 Domestic violence incidents</li>
    <li>🚨 Missing persons (especially children or vulnerable adults)</li>
    <li>🚨 Threats to life or property</li>
    <li>🚨 Suspicious packages or bomb threats</li>
    <li>🚨 Public disturbances or riots</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Non-Emergency (Visit Police Station):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>📋 Making a police report for documentation</li>
    <li>📋 Reporting lost items or documents</li>
    <li>📋 Reporting scams, fraud, or cybercrime</li>
    <li>📋 Applying for police clearance certificates</li>
    <li>📋 Reporting minor traffic accidents (no injuries)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="making-police-report">How to Make a Police Report</h2>
  <h3>In Person:</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to the nearest police station</li>
    <li>Bring your identification (MyKad, passport)</li>
    <li>Provide details: what, when, where, who</li>
    <li>Review the report before signing</li>
    <li>Keep a copy for your records</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Online (for certain crimes):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>e-Polis</strong> - Traffic accident reports</li>
    <li><strong>CCID Portal</strong> - Commercial crime reports</li>
    <li><strong>MCMC</strong> - Cybercrime reports</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="documents-needed">Documents Required</h2>
  <p>When visiting a police station, bring:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Original and copy of MyKad (Malaysians) or passport (foreigners)</li>
    <li>Supporting documents (photos, receipts, screenshots, etc.)</li>
    <li>Witness contact information (if applicable)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="your-rights">Your Rights When Dealing with Police</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Right to know why you are being questioned</li>
    <li>✅ Right to remain silent (except for basic identification)</li>
    <li>✅ Right to legal representation</li>
    <li>✅ Right to an interpreter if you don't understand Malay/English</li>
    <li>✅ Right to inform family members if detained</li>
    <li>✅ Right to medical examination if injured</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="specialized-units">Specialized Police Units</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>CCID (Commercial Crime Investigation Dept)</strong> - Fraud, scams, cybercrime</li>
    <li><strong>Narcotics Crime Investigation Bureau</strong> - Drug-related crimes</li>
    <li><strong>Special Branch</strong> - National security</li>
    <li><strong>Traffic Police</strong> - Road safety and accidents</li>
    <li><strong>SEA (Special Elite Action)</strong> - Counter-terrorism</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="community-policing">Community Policing</h2>
  <p>PDRM operates community policing programs:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>SUKARELAWAN POLIS (SUKSIS)</strong> - Volunteer police</li>
    <li><strong>Rukun Tetangga</strong> - Neighborhood watch</li>
    <li><strong>Police-Community Dialogue Sessions</strong> - Regular meetings</li>
  </ul>
`;

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "Do I need to pay to make a police report?",
    answer: "No, making a police report is completely free. Beware of anyone asking for payment."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I make a police report in English?",
    answer: "Yes, most police stations can handle reports in English or Malay. Larger stations may have officers who speak Chinese or Tamil."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does it take to get a police report copy?",
    answer: "You should receive a copy immediately after making the report. Keep this safe as you'll need it for insurance or other purposes."
  },
  {
    question: "What if the police station is too far?",
    answer: "You can make reports at any police station, not just the one in your area. Some reports can also be made online."
  }
];

const headings = [
  { id: 'what-is-pdrm', title: 'What is PDRM?', level: 2 },
  { id: 'emergency-numbers', title: 'Emergency Numbers', level: 2 },
  { id: 'when-to-call', title: 'When to Call Police', level: 2 },
  { id: 'making-police-report', title: 'How to Make a Police Report', level: 2 },
  { id: 'your-rights', title: 'Your Rights', level: 2 },
  { id: 'specialized-units', title: 'Specialized Units', level: 2 },
];
---

<Layout title={`${articleData.articleTitle} | People's Guide | EduLaluan`}>
  <Header />

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section 
      class="relative overflow-hidden py-section-lg border-b"
      style={{
        '--section-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,
        'border-bottom-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`
      }}
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <!-- Breadcrumb -->
          <Breadcrumb items={[
            { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
            { label: "People's Guide", href: '/panduan-rakyat' },
            { label: `Section ${articleData.sectionNumber}`, href: `/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}` },
            { label: articleData.articleTitle }
          ]} />

          <!-- Back Button -->
          <a
            href={`/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}`}
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-6"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
            </svg>
            Back to Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}
          </a>

          <!-- Article Title -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mt-6">
            <div 
              class="flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-3xl"
              style={{ 
                'backgroundColor': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,
                'color': 'white'
              }}
            >
              {articleData.sectionIcon}
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-1 tracking-wide uppercase">
                Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}: {articleData.sectionTitle}
              </p>
              <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
                {articleData.articleTitle}
              </h1>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mt-3">
                {articleData.articleDescription}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <section class="py-section-md bg-surface">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Main Content -->
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <!-- Audience Tabs (Simple/Detailed) -->
            <AudienceTabs>
              <Fragment slot="simple" set:html={simpleContent} />
              <Fragment slot="detailed" set:html={detailedContent} />
            </AudienceTabs>

            <!-- FAQ Section -->
            <div class="mt-12">
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
                Frequently Asked Questions
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                {faqs.map((faq) => (
                  <details
                    class="group rounded-xl border bg-surface-elevated transition-all"
                  >
                    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 font-semibold text-foreground list-none">
                      {faq.question}
                      <svg
                        class="h-5 w-5 text-muted-foreground transition-transform group-open:rotate-180"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                      >
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                      </svg>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-muted-foreground">
                      {faq.answer}
                    </div>
                  </details>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Last Updated -->
            <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border">
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                <strong>Last updated:</strong> {articleData.lastUpdated}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Table of Contents (Sidebar) -->
          <aside class="sticky top-24 hidden lg:block w-64 shrink-0">
            <nav class="space-y-1" aria-label="Table of contents">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">
                On This Page
              </h3>
              {headings.map((heading) => (
                <a
                  href={`#${heading.id}`}
                  class="block py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"
                  style={{ paddingLeft: `${(heading.level - 2) * 12 + 12}px` }}
                >
                  {heading.title}
                </a>
              ))}
            </nav>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation Footer -->
    <section class="py-section-md bg-background">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-surface-elevated p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted-foreground">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-sm">
                <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide provides general information only. Always verify with official sources for the most current information.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Section padding utilities */
  :root {
    --section-padding-lg: clamp(3rem, 5vw + 1rem, 5rem);
    --section-padding-md: clamp(2rem, 3vw + 1rem, 3rem);
  }

  .py-section-lg {
    padding-top: var(--section-padding-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--section-padding-lg);
  }

  .py-section-md {
    padding-top: var(--section-padding-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--section-padding-md);
  }

  /* Article Typography */
  .prose-panduan {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .prose-panduan ul,
  .prose-panduan ol {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose-panduan li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose-panduan a {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .prose-panduan a:hover {
    color: var(--primary-dark);
  }

  .prose-panduan strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan .bg-muted {
    background-color: var(--muted);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
</style>
